animal: Unique ingredients such as prebiotics and probiotics
desc_header: The crunchy Prins Protection Croque Mini kibble provides the right preventative support from puppy to senior.
description: Protection Croque Mini is specifically tailored to meet the needs of small dogs (>10 kg) and is enriched with prebiotics and probiotics, herbs, Schussler cell salts and other supportive ingredients for a healthy intestinal flora, supple muscles and joints and a healthy heart function. Schussler cell salts are not actual salts, but substances (minerals) found in the body. To provide body cells with the right materials needed to function properly, these cells need to present in a certain amount in the body.

EAN: Highly suitable for the family dog
desc_header: 100% natural, crunchy food for your family dog.
description: The Prins Fit Selection line consists of complete, healthy food that contains high-quality and highly digestible ingredients, ideally suited to keep the family dog in optimum condition. The appetising crunchy kibble promotes chewing, so the feed is better ingested.
